title: Hannah Waddingham
itunes:title: Hannah Waddingham
description: Hannah Waddingham has built an incredible career in the performing arts - whether it’s theatre, film, television or music, her diverse talents are at the forefront of every performance. Hannah currently stars alongside Jason Sudeikis in the surprise hit "Ted Lasso," vividly tapping into emotions and experiences that SO many of us can relate to.
